snippet.title: Vampire Slayer: The Resurrection Trailer.
snippet.description:
Vampire Slayer: The Resurrection is a faced paced, team based multiplayer FPS with two completely different teams, vampires and slayers.
Coming to Nintendo Switch 22nd December 2022 (Japan), 2nd January 2023 (USA & EU). Coming to Playstation 4/5, Steam and Xbox X|S soon.
